# Services directory

Holds non-React modules that the React app uses:

- `firebase.ts` — Firebase web SDK init + auth helpers (added in commit 2)
- `kloBrain.ts` — Maria AI concierge client (added in commit 3)
- `telegram.ts` — Telegram bot helpers (added in commit 3 if needed)

Imports use the `@/` alias defined in `tsconfig.json`, e.g.
`import { auth } from '@/services/firebase'`.
